wird die diskursive Bearbeitung zentraler Kategorien der Kritischen Theorie Ende der 1960er Jahre rekonstruiert. Die Studie stellt insofern die diskursive Bedeutungskonstituierung eines, die Politik- und Gesellschaftsgeschichte des 20. Jahrhunderts nachhaltig beeinflussenden, Demokratiekonzepts dar.  aThis study brings linguistic history and contemporary history together. Using the tools of discourse analysis it examines the linguistic quality of upheaval in the critical discourse of the late 1960s and considers the concepts of democracy represented in this discourse. The critical theory of the Frankfurt School serves as the point of reference in which these concepts are based. The book is aimed not only at linguists but also at historians and sociologists.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aCritical discourse analysisxPolitical aspectszGermany. 0aDemocratizationzGermanyy20th century. 0aGerman languagexDiscourse analysis. 4aDiskursanalyse. 4aPolitische Sprache. 4aSprachgeschichte. 7aFOREIGN LANGUAGE STUDY / German.2bisacsh  aDiscourse Analysis.  aLanguage History.  aPolitical Language.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2012z9783110288995oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2012z9783110288896oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978311026342840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311026343540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110263435423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110263435/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGAb2012